headline: 'Politicians only for themselves'
description: The Movement for Quality Government in Israel blasted the Knesset's approval of the so-called Jobs Law, saying politicians have "proved once again they are working only for themselves and for those who can ensure their re-election." (Attila Somfalvi)
articleBody: The Movement for Quality Government in Israel blasted the Knesset's approval of the so-called Jobs Law, saying politicians have "proved once again they are working only for themselves and for those who can ensure their re-election." (Attila Somfalvi)
title: הרומן שלי עם האנה: המתלבשת שחיה ונושמת את שנות ה-40
